Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A spaceship called Memorial is traveling around the world right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will be arriving in Japan in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When it is anchored, they are going to invite elementary students and let them see the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, great. I want to do that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't, Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:02:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only elementary students who won the writing contest are allowed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-You have to write an essay? -Yeah! It has to be about your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never dreamt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I already finished researching about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you would surely win the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get aboard as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spaceship in Imminent Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I want to be a botanist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and make huge and small flowers at my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If this works out, I will be able to make huge carrots
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and huge radish,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and help people in starvation in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, how was mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom? I'm sorry, but I think you misunderstood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Misunderstood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream is a state of being hallucinated while asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is different from one's personal behavior while awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a fool, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When we said "My Dream", did you think it was about a dream you get while asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dream about your future as in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what you want to do when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream about my future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never thought about that since you're a robot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a dreamful boy in that sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go into that spaceship. Isn't that right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have so many misspellings that I can barely read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So Midori Hayashi will go from our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kenichi Tezuka! -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,These two will go aboard the spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good for them. -Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know how to explain that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Osamu work so hard like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he has a dream of becoming a baseball player.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But teacher, I don't have to work that hard to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibukaki is lifting weights like that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because he wants to be a sumo wrestler in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But teacher, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Noboru wants to be a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, throw this with all your strenght.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, it's difficult to teach a robot about "dream".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If I become human, can I have dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure whether you can become one, but anyone can have dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'm not having any dream since I can do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and talk with Dr.Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want me to disable your super powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be human. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Atom? Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To this ship Memorial?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But since I have no dream, I couldn't write an essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, please. Please make me human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can disable your powers for a little while, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That will do. I want to have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. All right, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of experience could help you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done, Atom. Now get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, now I'm like a human being, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Try lifting that as a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy now, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you can't fly nor use your machine gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And Atom,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say you want to go back in the middle, I can't fix you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to stay like that for 24 hours. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So for 24 hours, I'm like a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble! Trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher! Sir! -What's wrong, Shibukaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher, Atom must have gone crazy. -Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Over there. -What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's "trying" to become a skydiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he's got a goal now, but he can fly anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have to practice or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, things have changed. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Use your jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! You fool! What have you done...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Why didn't you use your jet before you landed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I asked Dr.Ochanomizu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to disable my powers for 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become like my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But... If you do something wreckless like this, you will be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to become human, you should have considered that as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be back. I'll get some postcards for you as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky are Kenichi and Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the first place next year and get aboard the Ship Memorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You will go back to original Atom in three hours anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Three hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atom. Don't you want to get aboard the spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then, it's done! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have to look around politely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This elevator is 300 meters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is connected to the lobby of this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, how amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This lobby is the work of the world's best interior designer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We could play baseball here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that. It's so high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't play around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A spaceship that you can use to travle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,must be much fancier than a cruise ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Amazing. -Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Over here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for a visit? They are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes! Excuse me. -Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the controlling station. Only staff can enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So this ship, Memorial, doesn't need to anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for about three months once it takes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why all kinds of recreation facilities are equipped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In this room, you can watch recent news, 3D movies, animes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I can't watch it because of your shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice is Shibukaki's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Are you going to let the kids get into this as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice. Now we are all on the same boat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Move. Let the spaceship take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never do such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to destroy this stupid machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of reckless thing are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off immediately! Once we are back at school, I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Memorial just moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Memorial is taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There was no such plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right, Atom. -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we don't have to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is flying for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Maybe they are flying this as a special service for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Memorial has just been hijacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hijacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What does 'hijacked' mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It means this spaceship has been abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who did it? -He's in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot must have been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! You! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally succeeded. Now I can ignite a fire on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... How can he hijack our dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijacked Memorial is heading to Megapolis right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The cockpit is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I can easily take this door...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, it's weird. I have no strength in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You disabled your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I turn them back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to wait for time to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are about 25 minutes remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At a moment like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rescue team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You broke the meter but now I can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... I was going to fly to the end of space and die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Dang it! I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan always fails right before its success.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the net is going to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there is some luck remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You hijacker! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the injured one out. I'll be your hostage instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Send the other one in. I'll let the pilot go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I'll go instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You are just a kid. Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher! -Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's just a kid. -I'm the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency. Memorial ship which lost its control
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,has finally invaded Megapolis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, give up. The controller is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless it bumps against something, it will never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister. Why did you do such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in saying that now, but kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an unfortunate one like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You got shoved into a criminal's room like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right. I walked in here upon my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, that's even more unfortunate. You must have so many dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a powerful robot again in 10 minutes anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot? Are you a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lucky to be human. You can dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Because of that dream, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept making failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At firsst, I tried a transpacific, nonstop flight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with a solar-powered plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was about to land, the forecast went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I stopped in the middle of the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell because I ran out of battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I tried digging a gold mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, a huge earthquake took place
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and that big gold mine disappeared into underground soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed at every attempt to achieve my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonetheless, I'm jealous of people who can dream, even if they could fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lucky. You have tons of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you fail, you can always pursue your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The building is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Building! The big building is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One more minute. My power will come back after a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back. My powers are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The spaceship changed its direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Atom. Atom's powers are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The criminal got arrested and the kids were rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We avoided a big accident. Atom saved us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Teacher, did Atom win the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon? Yes, of course! He won the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! First place! First!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I hope Atom doesn't have weird dreams anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I like being a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I can't have dreams like human beings do,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more convenient to have my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom. Your powers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,also enable human beings to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Enable them to dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So I'm giving them dreams instead of having dreams myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Memorial ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it will really begin its around-the-world flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In this town of Sparitz, Germany,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a strange rock that resembles a human face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone calls it "Inmen Jiwa".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that a town will perish if this rocks turns away to the West?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious robot has a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Who made an explosion underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Inmen Jiwa is falling. The dam's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do? The town is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Inmen Jiwa"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:24:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
